node.content: ["One person has been critically injured and flown to hospital following a crash between a car and a motorcycle at \u014cmokoroa in western Bay of Plenty.", "Emergency services were alerted just after midday to the crash on Omokoroa Road.", "The road is closed and motorists are advised to avoid the area if possible as there are no alternative routes."]
